                      <p>This example has been created by retyping the first paragraphs of Annie Dillard's The Writing Life (1989), it is only intended to serve as an example of the visualisations.</p>
                      <p>Original text: Annie Dillard, <emph rend="italics">The Writing Life</emph> (1989)</p>
