          <text>
              <body>
                  <p source="keystrokes"><add seq="000001" type="nt" evidence="3">When you write, you lay out a line of words. </add><add seq="000013" type="nt" evidence="49">The line of words is a <del seq="000019" type="typo" evidence="73">i</del></add><add seq="000019" type="nt|continue" evidence="74">miner's pick<add seq="000034" type="context" evidence="103">, a woodcarver's gouge, a surgeon's probe</add>. </add><add seq="000025" type="nt" evidence="89">You wield it,<mod seq="000052" type="continue" evidence="145"> and it digs a path you follow. </mod></add><add seq="000116" type="nt" evidence="178">Soon you find yourself deep in new territory. </add><add seq="000151" type="nt" evidence="225">Is it <del seq="000212" type="context" evidence="264">worth it</del><add seq="000214" type="context" evidence="272">a dead end</add><add seq="000239" type="context" evidence="323">, or have you located the real subject</add>?</add> <add seq="000200" type="nt" evidence="243">You will know <del seq="000224" type="context" evidence="283">later</del><add seq="000225" type="context" evidence="288">tomorrow, or this time ne<del seq="000233" type="typo" evidence="314">t</del></add><add seq="000234" type="context|continue" evidence="315">xt year</add>.</add></p>
              </body>
